        ExplP3:
          "Today enjoy a half day excursion to the Absheron Peninsula, visiting the Ateshgah (or place of fire) a Zoroastrian Fire Temple, UNESCO Heritage site and natural burning mountain Yanardagh. Also see the medieval fortress in Mardakan, which in medieval times formed part of the defence system of the Peninsula and the attractive mosque at Amirjan.",
