        specailH2:
          "LAUDED FOR ITS EXTENSIVE KNOWLEDGE, ITS EAST-MEETS-WEST MODEL AND VENTURING RESPONSIBLY INTO EVERY CORNER OF ITS DESTINATIONS, IT IS OUR MISSION TO SHOW GUESTS THE BEATING HEART OF OUR ASIA",
